
The game of life (John Horton Conway's)
---------------------------------------

Evolving cellular automation based on neighbour population.

Dependencies:
* python 2.7
* Zelle's graphics.py
* Tk


Known Issues:
-------------

* crashes on quit (before starting)
* cannot stop once started
* cannot quit once started


Improvements:
-------------

UI improvements

* speed options
* restart (stop and clear)
* pause/continue
* place more pieces during pause
* save/place patterns
* end of simulation detection
    -> no changes
    -> looping
* screen dimensions
* screen location
* click+drag -> light up sets of cells


Architecture improvements

* get rid of copyList/statusList -> maintain list of cells to change
* Improve use of libraries
* Move away from graphics.py
* collapse frame classes into one

